==English==
===Etymology===
Prefix ''[[Afro-]]'' meaning "African", plus ''[[Argentinian]]'' from the country [[Argentina]]

===Adjective===
'''Afro-Argentinian'''

# Of or related to Afro-Argentinians.

====Synonyms====
* [[Afro-Argentine]]

===Noun===
''an'' '''Afro-Argentinian''' (''plural'': '''[[Afro-Argentinians]]''')

# An Argentine with African ancestry.

